      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must be under version control with documented regression test suite covering blood pump flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R1 used under ISO 9001-certified QMS. Regression tests documented for rotating machinery applications. Version control confirmed via internal audit log."
